{
  "texts": [
    "3.3.4 System prompt.",
    "The system prompt is the set of instructions defining the general task assigned to the LLM and is independent of the specific window being considered.",
    "Our prompt first asks the LLM to act as an activity recognition system.",
    "Then, it provides information about the rooms in the smart home, the main interactions with the environment that can be captured by the available sensors, and the list of activities of interest.",
    "Since this information depends on the specific smart environment and application, it must be provided during the installation phase."
  ]
}